# Image search API keys — used when creating a new game card to find a
# relevant photo via the Game / Activity Name. Sources are tried in order:
# Pexels → Unsplash → Pixabay → local fallback. A source with no key is
# silently skipped (with a console warning).
#
# Either name works for each key — vite.config.js reads both. Spec form
# (no prefix) is preferred:
#
# Pexels:   https://www.pexels.com/api/
PEXELS_API_KEY=
# Unsplash: https://unsplash.com/developers
UNSPLASH_ACCESS_KEY=
# Pixabay:  https://pixabay.com/api/docs/
PIXABAY_API_KEY=
